[{"id":"RAW_ee3ae4fb","title":"Nano Banana 2：将 Pro 级能力与闪电般的速度相结合","link":"https://deepmind.google/blog/nano-banana-2-combining-pro-capabilities-with-lightning-fast-speed/","date":"2026-02-26 16:02:08","oneSentenceSummary":"Google DeepMind 发布 Nano Banana 2 (Gemini 3.1 Flash Image)，这是一款具备搜索增强世界知识和先进主体一致性的高速图像生成模型。","summary":"Google DeepMind 推出了 Nano Banana 2，亦被称为 Gemini 3.1 Flash Image。该模型旨在以 Flash 架构极快的速度提供 Pro 级别的先进推理能力和视觉质量。关键技术亮点包括集成实时网络搜索以实现图像的事实溯源、改进的文本渲染与本地化，以及在多次生成中保持多达 5 个角色一致性的能力。该模型支持高达 4K 的分辨率，并正被集成到 Google 的生态系统中，包括 Gemini 应用、搜索和 Vertex AI。此外，文章还强调了通过 SynthID 水印和 C2PA 元数据实现的安全性。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ee3ae4fb.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Google DeepMind Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":4,"score":94},{"id":"RAW_077cbcec","title":"OpenClaw + Claude Code 超强教程：一个人就能搭建完整的开发团队！","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyNjM2MzQyNg==&mid=2247719868&idx=1&sn=c93e0542f8bebb653559315d02841b43","date":"2026-02-25 14:15:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_077cbcec.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Datawhale","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_fa264a88","title":"从上下文到长期记忆：大模型记忆工程的架构设计与实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651276307&idx=2&sn=bc69ed3bd600142d4e67f1a5df1103f4","date":"2026-02-25 07:46:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_fa264a88.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":38,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_e73edd69","title":"我们如何在一周内用 AI 重构 Next.js","link":"https://blog.cloudflare.com/vinext/","date":"2026-02-24 20:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_e73edd69.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Cloudflare Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_3879b2af","title":"1500 个 PR、0 人写代码：Codex 驱动的百万行级内部产品实践","link