e_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c16f8d46.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"dbaplus社群","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_97909516","title":"知识引导","link":"https://martinfowler.com/articles/reduce-friction-ai/knowledge-priming.html","date":"2026-02-24 14:40:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_97909516.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Martin Fowler","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_311e8fbb","title":"[AINews] Nano Banana 2 即 Gemini 3.1 Flash Image Preview：全新的 SOTA 图像生成模型","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/ainews-nano-banana-2-aka-gemini-31","date":"2026-02-27 04:39:57","oneSentenceSummary":"本期 AINews 摘要重点介绍了 Google Nano Banana 2 (Gemini 3.1 Flash Image) 的发布、智能体编程工作流的进展、Perplexity 与三星的集成，以及 Anthropic 与五角大楼之间的治理冲突。","summary":"本文全面回顾了 2026 年 2 月下旬的主要 AI 发展。重点包括 Google Nano Banana 2 (Gemini 3.1 Flash Image Preview) 的发布，该模型在图像生成排行榜上名列第一，同时价格远低于竞争对手。文章还涵盖了智能体编程的演进，指出工具正转向“基于任务”的委派和持久化记忆，尽管这引发了对代码复杂度债务的担忧。此外，文章详细介绍了 Perplexity 向三星硬件的战略扩张及其开源嵌入模型的发布。最后，文章探讨了 Anthropic 与美国国防部在 AI 军事用途方面重大的伦理和法律僵局。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_311e8fbb.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":6,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_9fbeb19b","title":"2026-02-26 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-26-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-26 08:17:43","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9fbeb19b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":78,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_08470002","title":"达利欧最新长文：2026，像极了 1936","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxNTAzNzU0Ng==&mid=2654903821&idx=1&sn=40f0a870f61197d0a83c71ea9add1fb2","date":"2026-02-25 13:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_08470002.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName"